{"tid":1368294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武唔係無腦","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:53.000Z","uid":160991,"like":135,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0505ac3273387fbe798883cbc70aa2987fda4f","tid":1368294,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"發夢每次都有去遊行<br />\n雖然唔係最勇武個批<br />\n但都堅持比較夜既時候<br />\n<br />\n點解而家見到有幾個post想帶個風向就係停1日勇武一定係大台?<br />\n咁樣叫和理非同勇武割蓆?<br />\n咁唔通我帶氣油彈帶刀話要殺警察?<br />\n其他人叫你唔好咁樣做<br />\n就叫做割蓆<br />\n<br />\n勇武唔係無腦<br />\n勇武係做普通市民有顧慮既 <br />\n而做出最大既利益<br />\n唔係叫你元朗企定定比人打<br />\n自衛一定係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但班黑社會要走一定早就走左<br />\n衝入人地條村打人拆祠堂<br />\n令一批本來都不齒黑社會既村民憎恨示威者<br />\n咁只不過係跌入群眾打群眾既陷阱<br />\n真正既報仇<br />\n係令到我地真正既目標達到<br />\n唔好為發洩而因小失大</span></strong>"},{"pid":"afbc6b70366a0a4c04b512518589001bb900d45b","tid":1368294,"uid":160991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"6dc5edbe3b4a5c49d29ece895532d1b9c31621cb","tid":1368294,"uid":190604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"5cbf404e7fef2a2243d12af3f5fcdf6bb905ac0c","tid":1368294,"uid":160991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"7138bb1a0839e3e226dbb5b228a521901d7e02af","tid":1368294,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"0ce42ab449265c27039b89c38c3a120fdb239946","tid":1368294,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8a966dbaf3eca65d10e6e1bf929eff0851b8bc1d","tid":1368294,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"24f0ae92f0f69c16808cba32fd7e9a812f16d17e","tid":1368294,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":